## Kyun Yeh Kaam Karta Hai:
```
n8n_data/*        → andar ki sab files ignore ✅
!n8n_data/.gitkeep → sirf yeh ek file upload ✅

GitHub pe folder dikhega
lekin sensitive data nahi ✅